---
// src/layouts/TelegramLayout.astro
---
<section class="flex flex-col gap-8">
  <header class="mb-4 animate-fade-in">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3">
      <i class="ri-quill-pen-line text-primary"></i>
      <span>时光碎片</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-2">一些随性的记录和不成熟的想法，漂浮在时间的河流里。</p>
  </header>
  
  <div id="dynamic-feed-container" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <slot />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>